<abstract><t>This draft describes a new TLS extension for transport of a DNS record set serialized with the DNSSEC signatures needed to authenticate that record set.  This allows TLS clients to perform DANE authentication of a TLS server without the need to perform additional DNS record lookups.</t></abstract>

